cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper presents a new algorithm for training deep learning models, specifically convolutional neural networks for image classification and recurrent neural networks for language tasks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Among these, machine learning (cs.LG) is the most likely sub-category as the paper focuses on a new optimization method for training deep learning models.
